data.description: CHILIWIST Immaculate 360 Mountain Views w/trees 6 miles from Malott. 2 Acre 1600+sqft single level home 4 bedroom/2.75 bath and oversized loft area for additional space. RV Parking. Warm & inviting entryway with closet, open living room w/wood stove & cascading windows from ceiling to floor, kitchen with newly done backsplash, fresh paint, new cabinets, & garbage disposal. Dining room off kitchen and coffee bar/nook area for additional counter space. Laundry/utility room with three-quarter bathroom. Primary bedroom with full bathroom en-suite. 3 additional bedrooms with plenty of closet space & full bathroom access. Stairwell leading to loft. Outside has fire pit/horseshoe pit. Septic. Private Well. Metal roof. $334,900 MLS-2152987/H-3176
